<configs>

	<!-- ==================================================================
	     Waka Ammo Flow Patch v0.1
	     ==================================================================
	     Targets Black Wolf better loot spawns ammo entries (the dominant
	     source of day 1-3 ammo flood). Vanilla entries are untouched.

	     Reduction schedule:
	       Small  : count x0.20-0.25, prob -2 steps (guaranteed->low, low->veryLow)
	       Medium : count x0.30-0.35, prob -1 step  (guaranteed->medLow, medLow->low)
	       Large  : count x0.50,      prob -1 step  (guaranteed->med, med->medLow)

	     Operation order: each entry uses 2 <set>s. The predicate matches
	     by @count value, so we change @loot_prob_template FIRST (predicate
	     still matches), then @count (which breaks the predicate but no
	     subsequent op needs it).
	     ================================================================== -->


	<!-- =========================== 9mm Small =========================== -->
